### 1. Create organization
POST http://localhost:8000/api/organizations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workspace_id": "demo-workspace",
  "name": "示例中医调理馆",
  "industry_type": "中医养生",
  "city": "杭州",
  "description": "一家专注睡眠、疲劳、体重管理的中医调理门店。",
  "target_audience": "35-50岁关注睡眠、疲劳和体重管理的女性",
  "core_services": "体质评估、睡眠调理、亚健康管理、体重管理",
  "compliance_notes": "避免承诺疗效，避免疾病治疗暗示。",
  "forbidden_words": "治愈,根治,保证,永久,7天见效,彻底改善"
}

### 2. Create material
POST http://localhost:8000/api/organizations/{{organization_id}}/materials
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workspace_id": "demo-workspace",
  "organization_id": "{{organization_id}}",
  "title": "产后睡眠和疲劳客户案例",
  "material_type": "客户案例",
  "source_type": "manual",
  "raw_text": "一位产后宝妈经常觉得累，晚上睡不好，白天没精神。她最担心的不是体重，而是怕身体状态越来越差。沟通后我们建议她先记录一周睡眠、饮食和情绪变化，再做基础评估。"
}

### 3. Analyze material
POST http://localhost:8000/api/materials/{{material_id}}/analyze

### 4. Generate topics
POST http://localhost:8000/api/organizations/{{organization_id}}/topics/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organization_id": "{{organization_id}}",
  "platform": "小红书",
  "conversion_goal": "引导咨询",
  "count": 5
}

### 5. Generate content task
POST http://localhost:8000/api/content-tasks/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organization_id": "{{organization_id}}",
  "topic_id": "{{topic_id}}",
  "content_type": "xiaohongshu",
  "platform": "小红书"
}

### 6. Compliance review only
POST http://localhost:8000/api/compliance/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organization_id": "{{organization_id}}",
  "input_text": "这个方法可以保证7天见效，彻底改善睡眠问题。"
}

